        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Tangguoa tongguling sp. nov., holotype male. A–B. Pedipalp (A. Prolateral view; B. Retrolateral view); C–D. Distal part of procursus (C. Prolateral view, arrows 1–5 indicate prolatero-ventral, ventral, distal, dorsal, and retrolateral apophysis, respectively; D. Retrolateral view). b = bulb, e = embolus, pr = procursus. Scale bars: 0.10 (A–B), 0.05 (C–D)." ;
